{"tid":1028935,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾加入ISIS產子後欲返英　「恐怖少女」正式褫奪國籍","createTime":"2019-02-20T00:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T08:10:53.000Z","uid":14918,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9cf9f0ce1f2c7b9c4dba1802dd4015ce35a7b436","tid":1028935,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T00:46:13.000Z","msg":"2015年加入極端組織ISIS的英國女子貝居姆（Shamima Begum）近日在敍利亞難民營產子後，表示希望返回英國生活。英國內政部周二（19日）書面通知她的家人，貝居姆的英國國籍已被褫奪。<br />\n家人感到失望正考慮上訴<br />\n<br />\n該封僅一頁的通知書收件人為貝居姆的母親，內裡提到，內政大臣賈偉德（Sajid Javid）決定褫奪貝居姆的英國國籍，希望她的家人能轉達消息，而貝居姆有權提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n貝居姆的律師阿康吉（Tasnime Akunjee）表示，貝居姆一家對裁決失望，正考慮上訴。<br />\n<br />\n有報道指出，貝居姆擁有英國和孟加拉的雙重國籍，因此英國才能剝奪其國籍，而又避免令她變成無國籍人士。不過，阿康吉否認，強調貝居姆只擁有英國國籍，「從未擁有孟加拉護照」。<br />\n<br />\n根據1981年英國國籍法令（British Nationality Act 1981）第40節，內政大臣有權以公眾利益為由褫奪國籍，但不得使該人士變成無國籍人士。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2460059/org/a7d3e3f733ffc60806c82f85ae9b99ae.JPG/yhVoLaJMkSs_GZjJSfTq3ezWFz5LINVbYHbtOWB27Tk?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2460059%2Forg%2Fa7d3e3f733ffc60806c82f85ae9b99ae.JPG%2FyhVoLaJMkSs_GZjJSfTq3ezWFz5LINVbYHbtOWB27Tk%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=377c5c88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0042c1aefb5fe92f293056102be7f88dcd015b6","tid":1028935,"uid":121146,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T00:48:04.000Z","msg":"佢嫁左比IS  咪敍利亞國藉囉屌 <br />\n最好趕走埋佢老母  全家都痴撚線"},{"pid":"afca83ee3e9b8ffb3136d2cc5427a8b0a20d39b4","tid":1028935,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T00:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52684dc08eddd3c1e28ab427f379dc7b065d486","tid":1028935,"uid":85461,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T00:51:37.000Z","msg":"God save our gracious Queen<br />\nLong live our noble Queen<br />\nGod save the Queen<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zln